module.exports = max

/**
 * Returns the maximum of two vec2's
 *
 * @param {vec2} out the receiving vector
 * @param {vec2} a the first operand
 * @param {vec2} b the second operand
 * @returns {vec2} out
 */
function max(out, a, b) {
    out[0] = Math.max(a[0], b[0])
    out[1] = Math.max(a[1], b[1])
    return out
}
